room_title: Escape room "Temple of the Lost Skull" by Escape Room Lafayette in Lafayette
room_address: 2429 W Congress St Suite C Lafayette, LA 70506
room_description:
You are on the trail of Dr. Reginald Brown, a renowned archaeologist. In all his travels and studies he had never seen anything like these artifacts he discovered recently! Most people believed them to be cursed...
Doctor Brown spent years following clues and searching for the history of these otherworldly objects. Their story led him to an isolated area of jungle that hadn't been inhabited by humans for thousands of years. In the Spring of 1956, Dr. Brown launched an expedition to discover their source. He entered the jungle...and was never seen or heard from again.
